BUTB

GENERATE BUTN SETUP

IC PARAM
IC SEED 1 H11 1 C1 1 C2
IC BUILD
IC FILL
IC PURGE
PRINT IC
PRINT COORD


bomblev -10 
! -------------------------------------------
! let's define the quantum part of the system
! -------------------------------------------
define qms sele BYNU 1:8 end

define mms sele .not. qms end

!prnlev 4

nbonds atom cutnb 12.0 ctofnb 11.0 ctonnb 10. 

quantum sele qms end glnk sele bynu 8 end -
!quantum sele qms end glnk sele bynu 10 end -
     am1 charge 0 scfc 0.00001 

energy

test first step 0.001

!mini abnr nstep 2   tolgrd 0.001 nprint 10

mulli

print coor

stop
